"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8727610-five-time-olympic-diving-medallist-daley-steps-down\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Five-time Olympic medallist Tom Daley has announced his retirement from diving.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.331852096856884e-52, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  The 30-year-old, who won gold at Tokyo in 2021, said he had decided to call time on his career in an interview with British Vogue.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6302666356437603, \"rank\": 0.5866296783905234, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.10855409443819e-35, \"text\": \"British Vogue\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's Daley, who claimed his fifth Olympic medal with silver in the 10m synchronised event in Paris last month, said: \\\"It feels very, very surreal.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9977588636921724, \"rank\": 0.00224616290462578, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999850660971, \"rank\": 1.4933833537690857e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure and expectations.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when I walked out and saw my husband (Lance) and kids (Robbie and Phoenix) and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.882343601274457, \"rank\": 0.07967065666975813, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9964933256285219, \"rank\": 0.003462926156975691, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley competed at five Games, making his bow at Beijing 2008 and winning gold and bronze in Tokyo, silver in Paris and bronzes in London and Rio.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6302666356437603, \"rank\": 0.5866296783905234, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999850660971, \"rank\": 1.4933833537690857e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999952483449, \"rank\": 4.641149045769371e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 13